Title: Homecoming (2)
Plot: The team returns to Jonas' homeworld when they learn that the Goa'uld are after its naquadria. When Jonas is captured by Anubis, Daniel is his only hope.
GuestStars: Gillian Barber, Doug Abrahams, Corin Nemec, Kevan Ohtsji, Cliff Simon, Adrian Hough, Glynis Davies, Jan Bos, Daniel Cudmore, Aaron Thompson
